    <h1>Welcome to <span>DYNAMITE FC</span></h1>
    <p id="top">
      Dynamite FC is an emerging football club based in the vibrant city of
      Springfield, known for its passionate fan base and commitment to community
      engagement. Established in 2015, the club has quickly made a name for
      itself in the local football scene, boasting a rich history of competitive
      spirit and sportsmanship. The club’s colors, bright orange and navy blue,
      symbolize energy and determination, reflecting the team’s dynamic playing
      style. Dynamite FC competes in the Springfield Football League and has
      consistently shown impressive performances, making it a formidable
      opponent. The team is known for its dedication to developing young talent,
      with a robust youth academy that nurtures aspiring players from the
      grassroots level. Under the leadership of head coach Mark Thompson, who
      has over 15 years of coaching experience, Dynamite FC emphasizes a
      disciplined approach to the game. The team’s tactical philosophy focuses
      on quick passing, high pressing, and fluid attacking play, which has
      earned them a loyal following. Key players, such as star striker Leo
      Martinez and skillful midfielder Sarah Johnson, have become fan favorites,
      often leading the charge in crucial matches. Beyond the pitch, Dynamite FC
      is deeply integrated into the Springfield community, organizing various
      outreach programs and charity events. The club hosts youth clinics,
      promotes healthy lifestyles, and supports local schools, fostering a sense
      of unity and pride among residents. As Dynamite FC continues to grow, its
      ambition remains clear: to achieve success on and off the field while
      inspiring the next generation of footballers. With a strong foundation and
      an unwavering commitment to excellence, the future looks bright for this
      exciting club.
    </p>
    <hr />
    <section id="container">
      <article id="one">
        <section class="mel">
          <img src="images/kick.png" alt="kicking  image" class="kick" />
        </section>
        <p class="para">
          Dynamite FC is a community-focused soccer club dedicated to fostering
          talent and promoting the love of the game at all levels. Established
          in 2010, we pride ourselves on providing a supportive environment for
          players of all ages. Our coaching staff is comprised of experienced
          professionals who are committed to developing both the skills and
          character of our players. We believe that soccer is not just about
          winning, but about teamwork, discipline, and building lifelong
          friendships.
        </p>
        <button>READ MORE</button>
      </article>

      <article id="two">
        <section class="mel">
          <img src="images/scout.png" alt="Scouting  image" class="kick" />
        </section>
        <p class="para">
          Scouting for talent is a pivotal part of our mission at Dynamite FC.
          We actively seek out young, passionate players who show potential and
          a love for the sport. Our scouting team attends local tournaments,
          school games, and community events to identify individuals who can
          contribute to our club’s growth. We aim to provide opportunities for
          players to showcase their abilities through our training camps and
          open tryouts, ensuring that all aspiring athletes have a chance to
          join our dynamic team.
        </p>
        <button>READ MORE</button>
      </article>

      <article id="three">
        <section class="mel">
          <img src="images/hardship.png" alt="mobile image" class="kick" />
        </section>
        <p class="para">
          Like many clubs, Dynamite FC has faced its share of hardships.
          Financial challenges and the impact of external factors such as the
          pandemic have tested our resilience. Despite these obstacles, we
          remain committed to our players and our community. We have implemented
          various fundraising initiatives and partnerships to sustain our
          programs and support our athletes. Looking ahead, we envision a future
          where Dynamite FC not only thrives on the field but also serves as a
          beacon of hope and inspiration for young athletes, encouraging them to
          pursue their dreams while upholding the values of teamwork, respect,
          and perseverance.
        </p>
        <button>READ MORE</button>
      </article>
    </section>

